+
+    Equation:
+        .. math::
+
+            atan2(x,y)=\left\{\begin{matrix}
+            & tan^{-1}(\frac{x}{y}) & y > 0 \\
+            & tan^{-1}(\frac{x}{y}) + \pi & x>=0, y < 0 \\
+            & tan^{-1}(\frac{x}{y}) - \pi & x<0, y < 0 \\
+            & +\frac{\pi}{2} & x>0, y = 0 \\
+            & -\frac{\pi}{2} & x<0, y = 0 \\
+            &\text{undefined} & x=0, y = 0
+            \end{matrix}\right.
